long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Play the classic arcade game Snake on your browser with Snake Game! Navigate the snake to eat food and grow longer, but be careful not to hit the walls or your own tail. With simple controls and retro graphics, Snake Game is a fun and addictive way to pass the time. 

Features include:

- Classic arcade gameplay
- Simple controls
- Retro graphics

Download Snake Game today and start playing the classic arcade game on your browser!
